org.jboss.aerogear.sync

Interface PatchMessage<T extends Edit<? extends Diff>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the Edit that this PatchMessage holds
    All Superinterfaces:
    Payload<PatchMessage<T>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiffMatchPatchMessage, JsonMergePatchMessage, JsonPatchMessage

    public interface PatchMessage<T extends Edit<? extends Diff>>
extends Payload<PatchMessage<T>>
    Represents a stack of changes made on the server of client side.

    A PatchMessage is what is passed between the client and the server. It contains a Queue of Edits that represent updates to be performed on the opposing sides document.
